<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email-container {
        border: 1px solid #007bff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      a {
        color: #007bff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h4>Welcome to the Military System</h4>
      <p>Hello <%= firstname %>,</p>
      <p>Your account has been created successfully. You can now go ahead and reset your password using your email address: <strong><%= email %></strong>.</p>
      <p>To reset your password, please <a href="https://military.com/login">click here</a>.</p>
      <p>If you need help, contact us at here.</p>
      <p>Regards,<br /><br /></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
